title: Signature(IPA)
text-main-provision: Choose mobile provision file for the main app
text-plugin-provision: Choose plugin provision file (Ignored if none plugin)
text-plugin-dialog-content: Select the description file matching the plugin
console-info:
iOS platform application signing is only supported on MacOS.
1. Prepare the application IPA package, P12 certificate, and provisioning profile for signing. If there are plugins, multiple profiles may be required.
2. Install the P12 certificate on your system.
3. Please refer to the document "Apple操作手册.pdf" for instructions on how to create the certificate and provisioning profile.
